title: I got the Silver Profile insignia, but I am gold.
body:
So I got to gold 3 in soloq, But I got the the Silver insignia. I think the problem is that I am silver in flex q and get the insignia form ther. I have a friend that only have a rank in soloq, and he got the gold insignia.

Hope there will come a fix to this :) 

Thanks in Advance

replies.body: I also got the silver insignia, but I am Plat V in SoloQue and I have Gold V in the flex ques. :/ but I was Silver 4 last Season.
Hmmm, I was also silver last Season, I think it migth be the problem??
So basically it's showing your rank from last season as you haven't actually received your rewards for this season yet, this can take up to a month to happen.

Hey guys, ranked rewards haven't distributed yet.  Bookmark our[ helpdesk thread ](https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/player-support/W0aEONuP-2017-ranked-rewards-help-desk)for updates on that progress.
